OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FIndia's Russia oil imports 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fjump tenfold, bank says    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, India's imports of Russian oil rose    
OL,6, tenfold last year, according to Indian 
OL,7, state-controlled lender Bank of Baroda.
OL,9,FThe figures show Asia's third largest  
OL,10,Feconomy saved around $5bn (#4bn) as it 
OL,11,Framped up crude purchases from Moscow. 
OL,13,FIt comes as Western countries have been
OL,14,Fcutting their imports of energy from   
OL,15,FRussia after its invasion of Ukraine.  
OL,17,FRussia has been selling energy at a    
OL,18,Fdiscount to countries like China and   
OL,19,FIndia, which is the world's third      
OL,20,Flargest importer of oil.               
